The motor drive device (<b>20</b>) also includes a regenerative braking and short-circuit braking switching controller (<b>25</b>) that may cause switching from (b) the regenerative braking connection configuration to (c) the short-circuit connection configuration, or vise versa.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>